            "creation_date": 1596890734,
            "body": "<p>This was introduced in java 11.<\/p>\n<p>If you have installed a JDK, you can call <code>javac<\/code> directly using the source file.<\/p>\n<pre><code>java &lt;Class&gt;.java\n<\/code><\/pre>\n<p>is basically the same as<\/p>\n<pre><code>javac &lt;Class&gt;.java\njava &lt;Class&gt;\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
            "answer_id": 63315564,
            "question_id": 63315541
        },
